title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Top 5 busiest airports - Finland
description:
In this video we will look at the top 5 busiest airports in Finland. This top 5 contains 5 airports which have been updated by the community so a lot of details can be seen when visiting those airports.

00:00 intro

10:54 Rovaniemi Airport
